<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Kolam Peluang Umum - NPA Smart System</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@500;700;900&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; background-color: #0f172a; color: white; }
        .font-m { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center pb-10">

    <!-- Header Section -->
    <div class="w-full bg-slate-900 border-b border-slate-800 p-6 pt-12 pb-16 text-center shadow-xl relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-[-50px] left-[-50px] w-40 h-40 bg-rose-500 rounded-full blur-[90px] opacity-20"></div>
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto relative z-10 space-y-4">
            <a href="index.html" class="inline-block bg-slate-800 text-slate-300 hover:text-white font-bold px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-xs mb-4 border border-slate-700 transition">
                &larr; KEMBALI KE DASHBOARD
            </a>
            <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white font-m uppercase tracking-wider">
                Kolam <span class="text-rose-400">Peluang Umum</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-slate-300 font-light">
                Pola copywriting Kuda Troya halus untuk masyarakat umum yang mencari penghasilan tambahan.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Content Section -->
    <div class="max-w-3xl w-full p-5 mt-6 relative z-20 space-y-6">
        
        <!-- Copywriting Card 1 -->
        <div class="bg-slate-800 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-700 shadow-lg">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400 font-m mb-2">Pola 1: Pendekatan Kasual (Teman Lama / Sahabat)</h2>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mb-4">Gunakan script ini untuk teman lama yang sudah lama tidak saling sapa.</p>
            
            <div class="bg-slate-900 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-700 relative">
                <p id="teks1" class="text-sm text-slate-300 whitespace-pre-line leading-relaxed">Halo [Nama], apa kabar nih? Udah lama nggak ngobrol ya.
                
                Eh, gue lagi jalanin project bisnis online nih, sistemnya udah disediain semua dan ada bimbingannya dari nol. Lumayan banget buat nambah pemasukan bermodal HP doang.
                
                Kalo lu lagi nyari peluang tambahan atau sekadar pengen tau buat cadangan income, kabarin ya, nanti gue share infonya.</p>
            </div>
            
            <button onclick="copyText('teks1', this)" class="mt-4 w-full bg-amber-500 hover:bg-amber-400 text-slate-900 font-bold py-3 rounded-xl transition uppercase text-sm font-m flex justify-center items-center gap-2">
                <span>📋</span> Salin Teks Ini
            </button>
        </div>

        <!-- Copywriting Card 2 -->
        <div class="bg-slate-800 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-700 shadow-lg">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400 font-m mb-2">Pola 2: Pendekatan Direct (Massal / Kontak Baru)</h2>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mb-4">Gunakan script ini untuk list kontak baru atau orang yang baru simpan nomor Anda.</p>
            
            <div class="bg-slate-900 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-700 relative">
                <p id="teks2" class="text-sm text-slate-300 whitespace-pre-line leading-relaxed">Halo Kak [Nama], salam kenal. Maaf mengganggu waktunya sebentar.
                
                Saya sedang mencari beberapa orang yang serius ingin membangun sumber penghasilan tambahan melalui bisnis digital. Sistem kami sangat ramah pemula dan bisa dikerjakan darimana saja tanpa mengganggu aktivitas utama.
                
                Jika Kakak sedang mencari peluang atau open mind terhadap income tambahan, saya izin membagikan detail sistemnya.</p>
            </div>
            
            <button onclick="copyText('teks2', this)" class="mt-4 w-full bg-amber-500 hover:bg-amber-400 text-slate-900 font-bold py-3 rounded-xl transition uppercase text-sm font-m flex justify-center items-center gap-2">
                <span>📋</span> Salin Teks Ini
            </button>
        </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="w-full text-center mt-12 mb-6">
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs font-light">
            &copy; 2026 NPA Smart System.<br>
            <span class="font-m font-bold">Developed by Sugiarto Kurniawan</span>
        </p>
    </footer>

    <!-- Scripts -->
    <script>
        function copyText(elementId, btnElement) {
            const textToCopy = document.getElementById(elementId).innerText;
            const originalBtnText = btnElement.innerHTML;
            
            navigator.clipboard.writeText(textToCopy).then(() => {
                btnElement.innerHTML = '<span>✅</span> Berhasil Disalin!';
                btnElement.classList.replace('bg-amber-500', 'bg-green-500');
                btnElement.classList.replace('hover:bg-amber-400', 'hover:bg-green-400');
                btnElement.classList.replace('text-slate-900', 'text-white');
                
                setTimeout(() => {
                    btnElement.innerHTML = originalBtnText;
                    btnElement.classList.replace('bg-green-500', 'bg-amber-500');
                    btnElement.classList.replace('hover:bg-green-400', 'hover:bg-amber-400');
                    btnElement.classList.replace('text-white', 'text-slate-900');
                }, 2000);
            }).catch(err => {
                console.error('Gagal menyalin teks: ', err);
                alert('Ups, gagal menyalin teks. Silakan coba lagi.');
            });
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
